    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在一个后启示录的世界中生存</h2></strong><strong>呼吸，如果你能的话...</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/e578effb1c2ae287cfc4889a45c2d390.poster.avif?t=1761916353\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/e578effb1c2ae287cfc4889a45c2d390.webm?t=1761916353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/e578effb1c2ae287cfc4889a45c2d390.mp4?t=1761916353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/2b0ce0d3dce84585a9eb65ca772fbc74.webp?t=1761916353\" width=600 height=8 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/7584cd6912abaa8129a32fb449b5005d.poster.avif?t=1761916353\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/7584cd6912abaa8129a32fb449b5005d.webm?t=1761916353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/7584cd6912abaa8129a32fb449b5005d.mp4?t=1761916353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/2b0ce0d3dce84585a9eb65ca772fbc74.webp?t=1761916353\" width=600 height=8 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/e94a40c531e033522beb39d0f4f7f6fa.poster.avif?t=1761916353\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/e94a40c531e033522beb39d0f4f7f6fa.webm?t=1761916353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/e94a40c531e033522beb39d0f4f7f6fa.mp4?t=1761916353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>⚔️ 与土匪、教徒、军人、精神病患者和动物战斗。<br>🗺️ 探索开放的世界并揭示其秘密。<br>🔍 找到将成为您庇护所的家并布置它。<br>🏕️ 生存，获取资源和食物。<br>🛠️ 制作武器、资源、药品和储备。<br>🎯 狩猎各种野生动物。<br><br>你将迎来一个巨大的世界，可以探索其中寻找不仅仅是空气，还有其他至关重要的资源：食物，水，武器和护甲。玩家可以追随不同的叙事路径，从简单的生存到与土匪互动和揭示这个被摧毁的世界的秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/e20b32cc0bac8f3f1c36172a3e45591f.avif?t=1761916353\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>生存是游戏的核心要素。玩家必须适应恶劣的条件，确保有足够的食物、水和庇护所，制作武器和护甲以保护自己免受野生动物、土匪和其他未知威胁的侵害。<br><br>在这个世界中，危险无处不在。缺乏空气，辐射区，具有攻击性的生物和敌对团体都可能导致你的死亡。除了物理威胁之外，玩家还将面临道德困境，可能改变故事的走向和他们生存的结局。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/c43dca20014a101d565b5f5d892e1942.avif?t=1761916353\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>在&quot;HOLD YOUR BREATH&quot;中，玩家不断面临在风险和潜在回报之间做出选择的抉择。冒险去危险中获取有价值的资源是否值得？是否应该信任陌生人？每个你做出的决定都可能产生长远的影响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360550/extras/700e32b2bfe2afd412edeabdd6bc958b.avif?t=1761916353\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>如果你准备面对一个每一口气都可能是你最后一口气的现实，那就深入&quot;HOLD YOUR BREATH&quot;的世界吧。选择在你手中：为每一升空气而战，还是屈服并成为这个无情世界的又一牺牲者。",
